data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located on the serene far East side of El Paso. Boasting 1,678 square feet of comfortable living space, this residence offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and cozy appeal. Step inside to discover a spacious layout featuring a well-appointed kitchen, ideal for culinary adventures and gatherings. Enjoy the tranquility of the surrounding area from the comfort of your private backyard. With its convenient location and ample space, this home invites you to experience the best of comfortable living in El Paso's East side.
